### Step 3: Implement Sniper and Bot Protection

Sniper bots are detrimental to fair tokenomics. Mitigate this with algorithms to detect and prevent suspicious transactions during early phases.

```solidity
// Enable a cooldown period to limit transactions immediately after launch
uint256 public tradeCooldown = 60; // Seconds
mapping(address => uint256) private lastTradeTime;

// Override transfer function to include cooldown
function _transfer(address sender, address recipient, uint256 amount) internal override {
    if(sender != owner()) {
        require(lastTradeTime[sender] + tradeCooldown < block.timestamp, "Cooldown in effect");
        lastTradeTime[sender] = block.timestamp;
    }
    super._transfer(sender, recipient, amount);
}
```

### Step 4: Integrate Rewards Structure

The reward system should align with actual user activity, ensuring that Leadership boards and gameplay dynamics are more enticing.

